{"id": 5813, "date": "1987-01-31T11:00:32", "date_gmt": "1987-01-31T19:00:32", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=5813"}, "modified": "2026-06-10T15:30:45", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-10T22:30:45", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-the-upstage-jam-band-the-blues-is-my-business", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/01/31/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-the-upstage-jam-band-the-blues-is-my-business/", "title": {"rendered": "The Blues is My Business"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>In 2003, songwriters Kevin Bowe and Todd Cerney wrote &#8220;The Blues Is My Business&#8221; for Etta James&#8217; Grammy-winning blues album,\u00a0<em>Let&#8217;s Roll.<strong>\u00a0</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/27cpSolK5Js?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>The song certainly caught Little Steven&#8217;s attention&#8211;he covered it for his latest album,\u00a0<em>Soulfire,\u00a0</em>and he&#8217;s been performing it all throughout his latest tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5hkwIB6XFMw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Shortly before the album was released, Steve, Bruce, Southside and a host of other assembled artists united on-stage at the Paramount Theater during the Asbury Park Music and Film Festival, forming a one-night-only ensemble called the Upstage Jam Band in honor of the legendary club.</p>\n<p>The first song Bruce, Steve, and co. played together? &#8220;The Blues is My Business,&#8221; and it remains the only time Bruce has performed the song to date.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/62786yIkVsc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>The Blues is My Business<br />\n</strong><strong>First performed:\u00a0</strong>April 21, 2017<br />\n<strong>Last performed:\u00a0</strong>April 21, 2017</p>\n<p>\u00a9 November 27, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Mere weeks before Little Steven released his cover of Etta James&#8217; &#8220;The Blues is My Business,&#8221; he and Bruce (and the rest of the Upstage Jam Band) covered it at the Paramount Theater in Asbury Park.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69726, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to